(42, 1, 38, 45, 4, 20, 21, 'be it unto me according to thy word', 'Faith and Acceptance of God''s Promise', 'This connection highlights the theme of faith in God''s promises. Both Mary and Abraham demonstrate a strong belief in what God has promised, with Mary accepting the angel''s message and Abraham being fully persuaded of God''s ability to fulfill His word.', 'theme', 0.391, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
